{"tid":1476153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮委任一個維吾爾人負責對華政策單野其實好好笑","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T17:21:55.000Z","uid":119393,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"20094ca1793d45941c1de8d2047ee663fdbba601","tid":1476153,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/08/14/why-a-new-trump-appointee-could-be-the-latest-sticking-point-between-the-u-s-and-china-uighur-american-director-nsc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2Fwhy-a-new-trump-appointee-could-be-the-latest-sticking-point-between-the-u-s-and-china-uighur-american-director-nsc%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=966dee07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/08/14/why-a-new-trump-appointee-could-be-the-latest-sticking-point-between-the-u-s-and-china-uighur-american-director-nsc/</a><br />\n<br />\n以往當有華裔響美國被委任做官既時候<br />\n中港傳媒即時狂煲猛播<br />\n又祖先係咩又鄉下係咩又採訪內地親戚之類<br />\n今次NSC搵個維吾爾人負責對華政策單野已經接近兩日<br />\n但仲未見中港傳媒有任務報導(可能入唔到集中營搵親戚)<br />\n咁係咩意思?<br />\n即係中國人潛意識唔當維吾爾人係中國人, 唔當係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(好啦臨post SCMP剛剛出左新聞)"},{"pid":"9a5e4140f916e110b2664900e46548d46241d2fc","tid":1476153,"uid":284565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:17:23.000Z","msg":"新疆其實真係一個好靚嘅地方，不過去過一次先知新疆有好多軍警mon 住曬 D 維吾爾族人，想入商場就可以逼你經金屬探測門，再搜你身果種。<br />\n<br />\n好希望我地可以俾個example，中國偏地開花。<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借推，大學生請幫個忙填問卷籌錢比612人道支援基金。<br />\n<br />\n問卷link： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=c7861317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6</a><br />\n<br />\n原post：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430200</a>"},{"pid":"05b51921738a55ccdf710a455cca64e460e126fb","tid":1476153,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"多族共融定漢族獨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n建議文宣組多宣傳：<br />\n- 齋坐齋企都可以塞爆港島<br />\n- 唔怕悶唔好走，一齊傾偈<br />\n- 怕影大頭就cap+超+口罩<br />\n- 唔自動上gear (有tear gas先上)<br />\n<br />\n818係要show團結，冇得行就坐爆維園，唔夠坐就坐爆港島<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475691\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475691</a><br />\n-分享自LIHKG討論區"},{"pid":"ea246d3e03b083124b5c37024dbf4ac3f73d0a6f","tid":1476153,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/08/14/why-a-new-trump-appointee-could-be-the-latest-sticking-point-between-the-u-s-and-china-uighur-american-director-nsc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2Fwhy-a-new-trump-appointee-could-be-the-latest-sticking-point-between-the-u-s-and-china-uighur-american-director-nsc%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=966dee07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/08/14/why-a-new-trump-appointee-could-be-the-latest-sticking-point-between-the-u-s-and-china-uighur-american-director-nsc/</a><br />\n<br />\n以往當有華裔響美國被委任做官既時候<br />\n中港傳媒即時狂煲猛播<br />\n又祖先係咩又鄉下係咩又採訪內地親戚之類<br />\n今次NSC搵個維吾爾人負責對華政策單野已經接近兩日<br />\n但仲未見中港傳媒有任<span style=\"color: red;\">何</span>報導(可能入唔到集中營搵親戚)<br />\n咁係咩意思?<br />\n即係中國人潛意識唔當維吾爾人係中國人, 唔當係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma